quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  36,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  36,1,Yaaseen
  36,2,qasam hai quran hakeem ki
  36,3,ke tum yaqeenan Rasolo-n mein se ho
  36,4,seedhay rastay par ho
  36,5,( aur yeh quran ) ghalib aur Raheem hasti ka nazil kardah hai
  36,6,taakay tum khabardaar karo aik aisi qoum ko jis ke baap dada khabardaar nah kiye gay thay aur is wajah se woh ghaflat mein parre hue hain
  36,7,"inn mein se aksar log faisla azaab ke mustahiq ho chuke hain, isi liye woh imaan nahi laatay"
  36,8,"hum ne unn ki gardnon mein taoq daal diye hain jin se woh thoriu taq jakray gay hain, is liye woh sir uthaye kharray hain"
  36,9,"hum ne aik deewar unn ke agay khari kar di hai aur aik deewar unn ke peechay hum ne inhen dhaank diya hai, inhen ab kuch nahi sujhta"
  36,10,"un ke liye yaksaa hai, tum inhen khabardaar karo ya nah karo, yeh nah manen ge"
  36,11,tum to usi shakhs ko khabardaar kar satke hi jo nasiyaat ki pairwi kere aur be dekhe khuday-e Rehman se daray ussay mughfirat aur ajar kareem ki basharat day do
  36,12,"hum yaqeenan aik roz mardon ko zindah karne walay hain jo kuch af-aal unhon ne kiye hain woh sab hum likhte ja rahay hain, aur jo kuch assaar unhon ne peechay chhorey hain woh bhi hum Sabt kar rahay hain har cheez ko hum ne aik khuli kitaab mein darj kar rakha hai"
  36,13,aِnhin misaal ke tor par uss bastii walon ka qissa sunaaoo jabkay uss mein rasool aeye thay
  36,14,"hum ne un ki taraf do rasool beje aur unhon ne dono ko jhutla diya phir hum ne teesra madad ke liye bheja aur un sab ne kaha"" hum tumhari taraf rasool ki hesiyat se beje gay hain """
  36,15,"bastii walon ne kaha"" tum kuch nahi ho magar hum jaisay chand ensaan, aur khuday-e rehman ne hargiz koi cheez nazil nahi ki hai, tum mehez jhoot boltay ho """
  36,16,"Rasolo-n ne kaha"" hamara rab jaanta hai ke hum zaroor tumhari taraf rasool bana kar beje gay hain"
  36,17,"aur hum par saaf saaf pegham pouncha dainay ke siwa koi zimma daari nahi hai """
  36,18,"bastii walay kehnay lagey"" hum to tumhe apne liye faal bad samajte hain agar tum baz nah aeye to hum tum ko sangsar kar den ge aur hum se tum barri dard naak saza pao ge """
  36,19,"Rasolo-n ne jawab diya"" tumhari faal bad to tumahray apne sath lagi hui hai kya yeh baatein tum iss liye karte ho ke tumhe nasiyaat ki gayi? asal baat yeh hai ke tum hadd se guzray hue log ho """
  36,20,"itnay mein shehar ke door daraaz gooshay seshakhs dorta howa aaya aur bola"" ae meri qoum ke logo, Rasolo-n ki pairwi ikhtiyar kar lau"
  36,21,pairwi karo unn logon ki jo tum se koi ajar nahi chahtay aur theek rastay par hain
  36,22,aakhir kyun nah mein uss hasti ki bandagi karoon jis ne mujhe peda kya hai aur jis ki taraf tum sab ko palat kar jana hai ?
  36,23,kya mein ussay chore kar dosray mabood bana lon? halaank agar khuday-e rehman mujhe koi nuqsaan pahunchana chahay to nah unn ki Shafaat mere kisi kaam aa sakti hai aur nah woh mujhe churra hi satke hain
  36,24,agar mein aisa karoon to mein Sarih gumraahi mein mubtala ho jaoon ga
  36,25,"mein to tumahray rab par imaan le aaya, tum bhi meri baat maan lau """
  36,26,"( aakhir kaar un logon ne usay qatal kar diya aur ) is shakhs se keh diya gaya ke"" daakhil ho ja jannat mein"" uss ne kaha"" kash meri qoum ko maloom hota"
  36,27,"ke mere rab ne kis cheez ki badolat meri mughfirat farma di aur mujhe ba izzat logon mein daakhil farmaya """
  36,28,is ke baad uss ki qoum par hum ne aasman se koi lashkar nahi utaara hamein lashkar bhejnay ki koi haajat nah thi
  36,29,bas aik dhamaka howa aur yakayak woh sab bujh kar reh gay
  36,30,"afsos bundon ke haal par, jo rasool bhi un ke paas aaya uss ka woh mazaq hi uratay rahay"
  36,31,kya unhon ne dekha nahi ke un se pehlay kitni hi qomon ko hum halaak kar chuke hain aur is ke baad woh phir kabhi un ki taraf palat kar nah aeye ?
  36,32,un sab ko aik roz hamaray samnay haazir kya jana hai
  36,33,inn logon ke liye be jaan zameen aik nishani hai hum ne is ko zindagi bakhsh aur is se ghalla nikala jisay yeh khatay hain
  36,34,hum ne is mein khajoron aur angarro ke baagh peda kiye aur is ke andar chashmay phore nikalay
  36,35,taakay yeh is ke phal khayen yeh sab kuch un ke apne hathon ka peda kya howa nahi hai phir kya yeh shukar ada nahi karte ?
  36,36,pak hai woh zaat jis ne jumla aqsam ke jore peda kiye khuwa woh zameen ki nabataat mein se hon ya khud inn ki apni jins ( yani noo insani ) mein se ya unn ashya mein se jin ko yeh jantay taq nahi hain
  36,37,"inn ke liye aik aur nishani raat hai, hum uss ke oopar se din hata dete hain to inn par andhera chhaa jata hai"
  36,38,"aur Sooraj , woh apne thikaane ki taraf chala ja raha hai yeh zabardast Aleem hasti ka baandha howa hisaab hai"
  36,39,"aur chaand, uss ke liye hum ne manzilain muqarrar kar di hain yahan taq ke un se guzarta howa woh phir khajoor ki sookhi shaakh ke manind reh jata hai"
  36,40,nah Sooraj ke bas mein yeh hai ke woh chaand ko ja pakdae aur nah raat din par Sabqat le ja sakti hai sab aik aik fallak mein teer rahay hain
  36,41,inn ke liye yeh bhi aik nishani hai ke hum ne inn ki nasal ko bhari hui kashti mein sawaar kar diya
  36,42,aur phir inn ke liye waisi hi kashtiyan aur peda kee jin par yeh sawaar hotay hain
  36,43,"hum chahain to inn ko ghark kar den, koi inn ki faryaad suneney wala nah ho aur kisi terhan yeh nah bachaaye ja saken"
  36,44,bas hamari rehmat hi hai jo inhen paar lagati aur aik waqt khaas taq zindagi se mtmta honay ka mauqa deti hai
  36,45,"inn logon se jab kaha jata hai ke bachcho uss injaam se jo tumahray agay aa raha hai aur tumahray peechay guzar chuka hai, shayad ke tum par reham kya jaye ( to yeh suni aَn suni kar jatay hain )"
  36,46,inn ke samnay inn ke rab ki ayaat mein se jo aayat bhi aati hai yeh is ki taraf iltifaat nahi karte
  36,47,"aur jab inn se kaha jata hai ke Allah ne jo rizaq tumhe ataa kya hai uss mein se kuch Allah ki raah mein bhi kharch karo to yeh log jinhon ne kufar kya hai imaan laane walon ko jawab dete hain"" kya hum unn ko khilain jinhein agar Allah chahta to khud khula deta? tum to bilkul hi behak gay ho """
  36,48,"yeh log kehte hain ke"" yeh qayamat ki dhamki aakhir kab poori ho gi? batao agar tum sachey ho """
  36,49,darasal yeh jis cheez ki raah taq rahay hain woh bas aik dhamaka hai jo yakayak aِnhin ain uss haalat mein dhar le ga jab yeh ( apne dunewi mamlaat mein ) jhagar rahay hon ge
  36,50,"aur uss waqt yeh wasiyat taq nah kar saken ge, nah apne gharon ko palat saken ge"
  36,51,phir aik sor phonka jaye ga aur yakayak yeh apne rab ke huzoor paish honay ke liye apni qabron se nikal parrin ge
  36,52,"ghabra kar kahin ge :"" arrey, yeh kis ne hamein hamari khawab gaah se uttha khara kya ?"" "" yeh wohi cheez hai jis ka khuday-e Rehman ne wada kya tha aur Rasolo-n ki baat sachhi thi """
  36,53,aik hi zor ki aawaz ho gi aur sab ke sab hamaray samnay haazir kar diye jayen ge
  36,54,aaj kisi par zarra barabar zulm nah kya jaye ga aur tumhe waisa hi badla diya jaye ga jaisay amal tum karte rahay thay
  36,55,aaj janati log mazay karne mein mashgool hain
  36,56,woh aur un ki biwiyan ghany saayon mein hain masnadon par takiye lagaye hue
  36,57,"har qisam ki lazeez cheeze khanay peenay ko un ke liye wahan mojood hain, jo kuch woh talab karen unn ke liye haazir hai"
  36,58,rab Raheem ki taraf se un ko salam kaha gaya hai
  36,59,"aur ae mujrimo, aaj tum chaatt kar allag ho jao"
  36,60,"aadam ke bachcho, kya mein ne tum ko hadaayat nah ki thi ke shetan ki bandagi nah karo, woh tumhara khula dushman hai"
  36,61,"aur meri hi bandagi karo, yeh seedha rasta hai ?"
  36,62,magar is ke bawajood is ne tum mein se aik giroh kaseer ko gumraah kar diya kya tum aqal nahi rakhtay thay ?
  36,63,yeh wohi jahannum hai jis se tum ko daraya jata raha tha
  36,64,jo kufar tum duniya mein karte rahay ho uss ki Padaash mein ab iss ka eendhan bano
  36,65,"aaj hum inn ke mun band kiye dete hain, inn ke haath hum se bolein ge aur un ke paon gawahi den ge ke yeh duniya mein kya kamaai karte rahay hain"
  36,66,"hum chahain to inn ki ankhen moond den, phir yeh rastay ki taraf lapak kar dekhen, kahan se aِnhin rasta sujhai day ga ?"
  36,67,hum chahain to aِnhin inn ki jagah hi par is terhan maskh kar ke rakh den ke yeh nah agay chal saken nah peechay palat saken
  36,68,"jis shakhs ko hum lambi Umar dete hain is ki saakht ko hum ulat hi dete hain, kya ( yeh halaat dekh kar ) inhen aqal nahi aati ?"
  36,69,hum ne iss ( nabi ) ko shair nahi sikhaya hai aur nah shairi is ko Zaib hi deti hai yeh to aik nasiyaat hai aur saaf parhi jaane wali kitaab
  36,70,taakay woh har uss shakhs ko khabardaar kar day jo zindah ho aur inkaar karne walon par Hujjat qaim ho jaye
  36,71,kya yeh log dekhte nahi hain ke hum ne apne hathon ki banai hui cheezon mein se inn ke liye maweshi peda kiye aur ab yeh un ke maalik hain
  36,72,"hum ne unhen is terhan inn ke bas mein kar diya hai ke unn mein se kisi par yeh sawaar hotay hain, kisi ka yeh gosht khatay hain"
  36,73,aur unn ke andar inn ke liye terhan terhan ke fawaid aur mashrobat hain phir kya yeh shukar guzaar nahi hotay ?
  36,74,yeh sab kuch hotay hue unhon ne Allah ke siwa dosray khuda bana liye hain aur yeh umeed rakhtay hain ke inn ki madad ki jaye gi
  36,75,woh inn ki koi madad nahi kar satke balkay yeh log ultay unn ke liye haazir baash lashkar banay hue hain
  36,76,"acha, jo baatein yeh bana rahay hain woh tumhe ranjida nah karen, inn ki chhupi aur khuli sab baton ko hum jantay hain"
  36,77,kya ensaan daikhta nahi hai ke hum ne usay nutfa se peda kya aur phir woh Sarih jhagralu ban kar khara ho gaya ?
  36,78,"ab woh hum par misalein chaspan karta hai aur apni paidaiesh ko bhool jata hai kehta hai"" kon un hadion ko zindah kere ga jabkay yeh boseedah ho chuki hon? """
  36,79,"is se kaho, aِnhin wohi zindah kere ga jis ne pehlay inhen peda kya tha, aur woh takhleeq ka har kaam jaanta hai"
  36,80,wohi jis ne tumahray liye harey bharay darakht se aag peda kar di aur tum is se apne cholhe roshan karte ho
  36,81,"kya woh jis ne asmano aur zameen ko peda kya iss par Qadir nahi hai ke inn jeson ko peda kar sakay? kyun nahi, jabkay woh maahir Khalaq hai"
  36,82,woh to jab kisi cheez ka iradah karta hai to is ka kaam bas yeh hai ke usay hukum day ke ho ja aur woh ho jati hai
  36,83,"pak hai woh jis ke haath mein har cheez ka mukammal Iqtidaar hai, aur isi ki taraf tum pulta-ay jaane walay"
